{"tid":533561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[食咗會上電]黑心商人用電池液浸50噸紅毛丹","createTime":"2018-01-19T01:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T11:45:52.000Z","uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f18287450e82cdc20616f0d185f24d06963d84a5","tid":533561,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T01:50:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1614635878680892/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1614635878680892%2F&d=6mpiucgFL%2B7RJizNolVLEr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=62e42adb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1614635878680892/</a><br />\n<br />\n有線中國組<br />\n2 hours ago &middot;<br />\nFollow<br />\n3-dots-h<br />\n【黑心商人用電池液浸50噸紅毛丹】<br />\n【食咗會上電？】<br />\n<br />\n湖南長沙記者揭發有黑心商人在一個倉庫用電池原液、金屬表面處理劑等化工原料，浸泡幾十桶紅毛丹合共50噸，目的是為容易變壞的紅毛丹保鮮。<br />\n<br />\n事件曝光後，工場負責人否認液體是化工原料，聲稱只是保鮮劑，「包裝上寫著不一定是那個東西」。<br />\n<br />\n負責人在被帶走調查的途中逃脫，更襲擊兩名執法人員致重傷，目前仍在追捕中。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個話鍾意耐唔耐去支那食好西</span></span>"},{"pid":"7f5260e8617933f1e6eeb20526912ff1baf0c5ee","tid":533561,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T01:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266c821bbaa45b8fef370216eefa2f68d2b50ac5","tid":533561,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T02:02:20.000Z","msg":"優美開始<br />\nJR"},{"pid":"82384ef68e9d2a26d701fcc9b4a2631cc38d0f80","tid":533561,"uid":68963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11:40:21.000Z","msg":"水？<br />\n<br />\n叫佢即場飲一啖啦"},{"pid":"cbbca7e1e2035393133e652367aa363a87b22182","tid":533561,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11